0budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20across%20the%20four%20food%20plans%2C%20the%20monthly%20budget%20recommendation%20has%20risen%2027%25%20since%20the%20start%20of%202020.%20Meanwhile%2C%20as%20of%20November%2C%20grocery%20prices%20were%20up%2025.1%25%20since%20the%20start%20of%202020%2C%20outpacing%20the%2018.9%25%20increase%20in%20overall%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20USDA%20changed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fproducts%2Fgao-23-105450%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformula%20for%20the%20thrifty%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20larger%20increase%20than%20the%20other%20cost%20levels.%20The%20average%20increase%20for%20the%20low%2C%20moderate%2C%20and%20liberal%20plans%20was%2023%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plans%20are%20designed%20to%20show%20how%20to%20have%20a%20healthy%20diet%20at%20various%20price%20levels%20for%20a%20family%20of%20four%2C%20defined%20as%20a%20male%20and%20a%20female%2C%20both%20between%2019%20and%2050%20years%20old%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20children%2C%20one%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20six%20and%20eight%20and%20the%20other%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20nine%20and%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FQ2mUS%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22USDA's%20recommended%20budget%20for%20a%20family%20of%20four%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22496%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20adjust%20for%20smaller%20households%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USDA%20has%20also%20broken%20down%20the%20recommended%20grocery%20budgets%20for%20individuals%20by%20sex%20and%20age%20based%20on%20recommended%20calories%20and%20nutrients%20during%20different%20stages%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20an%20adult%20male%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2019%20and%2050%20has%2