d%20War%20II%20and%20Desert%20Storm%2C%20where%20infantry%20and%20armor%20backed%20by%20airpower%20seized%20vast%20territory.%20But%20it's%20a%20future%20the%20West%20must%20prepare%20for%2C%20warns%20Alex%20Vershinin%2C%20a%20retired%20US%20Army%20lieutenant%20colonel%2C%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Fcommentary%2Fattritional-art-war-lessons-russian-war-ukraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessay%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Britain's%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20demonstrated%20that%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20now%20%E2%80%94%20firepower%20dominates%20maneuver.%20Russian%20and%20Ukrainian%20have%20painfully%20learned%20that%20with%20surveillance%20and%20attack%20drones%20constantly%20overhead%2C%20emerging%20from%20cover%20is%20dangerous%20and%20slow.%20Long-range%20guided%20missiles%20and%20shells%20can%20decimate%20armored%20columns%20that%20dare%20to%20thrust%20through%20minefields%20and%20layered%20defenses%20covered%20by%20artillery%20and%20airpower.%20Instead%20of%20sweeping%20offensives%2C%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20become%20a%20largely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-and-ukraine-bakhmut-battle-looks-like-stalingrad-expert-says-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatic%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20immense%20preparations%20are%20made%20for%20attacks%20that%20might%20gain%20an%20obscure%20village%20or%20a%20few%20square%20miles%20of%20territory%20before%20the%20attacker%20halts%20to%20dig%20in%20and%20regroup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20easier%20to%20mass%20fires%20than%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Vershinin%20said%20in%20the%20RUSI%20analysis.%20%26quot%3BDeep%20maneuver%2C%20which%20requires%20the%20massing%20of%20combat%20power%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20possible%20because%20any%20massed%20force%20will%20be%20destroyed%20by%20indirect%20fires%20before%20it%20can%20achieve%20success%20in%20depth.%20Instead%2C%20a%20ground%20offensive%20requires%20a%20tight%20protective%20bubble%20to%20ward%20off%20enemy%20strike%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShallow%20attacks%20along%20the%20forward%20line%20of%20troops%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20successful%20at%20an%20acceptable%20cost%20ratio%3B%20attempts%20at%20deep%20penetration%20will%20be%20exposed%20to%20massed%20fires%20the%20moment%20they%20exit%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20defensive%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vershinin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Patriot%20air%20defense%20system%20was%20test-fired%20during%20a%202017%20training%20in%20Greece.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661574dd16bde8d4ead6f918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Patriot%20air%20defense%20system%20was%20test-fired%20during%20a%202017%20training%20in%20Greece.%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Sweeney%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20moving%20shield%20would%20consist%20of%20layers%20of%20defense%20systems%2C%20including%20air%20defense%20against%20drones%20and%20missiles%2C%20as%20well%20as%20electronic%20warfare%20to%20jam%20those%20drones%20and%20missiles%20by%20flooding%20their%20control%20frequencies%20with%20electronic%20noise.%20But%20this%20protection%20comes%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20rapid%20maneuver.%20That%20bubble%20must%20be%20carefully%20set%20up%20to%20provide%20interlocking%20coverage%20against%20multiple%20types%20of%20threats%2C%20and%20move%20in%20lockstep%20with%20the%20column.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoving%20numerous%20interdependent%20systems%20is%20highly%20complicated%20and%20unlikely%20to%20be%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Vershinin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoordinating%20all%20these%20different%20weapons%20and%20jammers%20also%20requires%20skilled%20staff%20work%20that%20even%20advanced%20armies%20may%20lack.%20%26quot%3BIntegration%20of%20these%20overlapping%20assets%20requires%20centralized%20planning%20and%20exceptionally%20well-trained%20staff%20officers%2C%20capable%20of%20integrating%20multiple%20capabilities%20on%20the%20fly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vershinin.%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20years%20to%20train%20such%20officers%2C%20and%20even%20combat%20experience%20does%20not%20generate%20such%20skills%20in%20a%20short%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20example%2C%20Vershinin%20cites%20a%20hypothetical%20advance%20by%20a%20platoon%20of%2030%20soldiers.%20This%20would%20require%20multiple%20jammers%20to%20disrupt%20enemy%20drones%2C%20guided%20rockets%2C%20and%20communication%20systems.%20Engineers%20will%20have%20to%20clear%20a%20path%20through%20any%20minefields%2C%20and%20the%20infantry%20will%20have%20to%20coordinate%20with%20friendly%20artillery%20and%20drones.%20Failure%20to%20do%20this%20could%20be%20catastrophic%3A%20Russia%20is%20now%20firing%2010%2C000%20artillery%20shells%20per%20day%2C%20and%20this%20year%20it%20has%20already%20dropped%203%2C500%20big%20GPS-guided%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-in-a-race-to-stop-russia-glide-bomb-attacks-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglide%20bombs%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20devastated%20Ukrainian%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20systems%20need%20to%20work%20as%20an%20integrated%20team%20just%20to%20support%2030%20men%20in%20several%20vehicles%20attacking%20another%2030%20men%20or%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Vershinin%20said.%20The%20preparations%20needed%20for%20a%20brigade-%20or%20division-sized%20attack%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20are%20needed%20to%20achieve%20decisive%20victories%20on%20the%20battlefield%20%E2%80%94%20can%20only%20be%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20raises%20a%20deeper%20problem%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20West.%20Without%20maneuver%2C%20war%20becomes%20a%20battle%20of%20attrition%2C%20like%20the%20First%20World%20War%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nps.gov%2Fpete%2Flearn%2Fhistoryculture%2Fbattles.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esiege%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20with%20the%20Union%20and%20Confederate%20armies%20in%20front%20of%20Richmond%20in%201864.%20These%20kinds%20of%20wars%20are%20fought%20over%20years%20and%20cause%20slaughter%20on%20a%20massive%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20West%20is%20not%20prepared%20for%20this%20kind%20of%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Vershinin%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20most%20Western%20experts%2C%20attritional%20strategy%20is%20counterintuitive.%20Historically%2C%20the%20West%20preferred%20the%20short%20'winner%20takes%20all'%20clash%20of%20professional%20armies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20some%20extent%2C%20all%20wars%20are%20attritional%3A%20what%20ultimately%20destroyed%20the%20Third%20Reich%20wasn't%20a%20few%20defeats%20like%20Stalingrad%20and%20Normandy%2C%20but%20the%20cumulative%20losses%20from%20six%20years%20of%20relentless%20fighting.%20However%2C%20sustaining%20a%20war%20of%20attrition%20requires%20an%20emphasis%20on%20production%2C%20mobilizing%20resources%20for%20the%20long%20haul%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20continuously%20replace%20losses.%20Victory%20goes%20to%20the%20side%20that%20can%20wear%20down%20the%20enemy%20while%20maintaining%20its%20own%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20military%20conduct%20of%20war%20is%20driven%20by%20overall%20political%20strategic%20objectives%2C%20military%20realities%20and%20economic%20limitations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vershinin.%20%26quot%3BCombat%20operations%20are%20shallow%20and%20focus%20on%20destroying%20enemy%20resources%2C%20not%20on%20gaining%20terrain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20Western%20public%20will%20tolerate%20this%20mode%20of%20warfare.%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20his%20generals%20may%20not%20lose%20any%20sleep%20over%20suffering%20nearly%20500%2C000%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwar.ukraine.ua%2Ffaq%2Fwhat-are-the-russian-death-toll-and-other-losses-in-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecasualties%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20two%20years.%20But%20the%20average%20American%20or%20European%20may%20feel%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-armys-rapid-maneuver-may-be-over-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713088801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661574ef3f923f7dab05f0d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-armys-rapid-maneuver-may-be-over-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modern%20weapons%20have%20become%20so%20accurate%20and%20lethal%20that%20soon%20even%20the%20most%20advanced%20armies%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20maneuver%20rapidly%20on%20the%20battlefield.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-armys-rapid-maneuver-may-be-over-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20urges%20'restraint'%20after%20Iranian%20attack%20on%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713088585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-10928736