also%20the%20oldest%20of%20seven%20children%2C%20I%20believed%20I'd%20hit%20the%20jackpot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20our%20first%20date%2C%20I%20fixated%20on%20Neil's%20status%20as%20%26quot%3BGreg.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20never%20'The%C2%A0Brady%20Bunch%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20deadpanned.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20show%20that%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ealmost%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0came%20close%20to%20us%20was%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E'Eight%20Is%20Enough.'%20We%20all%20started%20to%20watch%20the%20first%20episode%20then%20my%20father%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20about%20a%20family%20with%20lots%20of%20kids%3F%20It's%20been%20on%20for%2030%20minutes%20and%20nobody's%20broken%20anything%20or%20had%20one%20argument.%20Turn%20this%20off.'%20And%20that%20ended%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeil's%20reality%20was%20not%20my%20fantasy%2C%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-do-you-know-when-youre-in-love-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20falling%20in%20love%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20of%20having%20siblings%20loomed%20large%2C%20even%20without%20Brady-like%20hijinks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22548%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20posing%20for%20photo%20in%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618559716bde8d4ead829b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20learned%20so%20much%20through%20my%20extended%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20four%20brothers-in-law%20and%20two%20sisters-in-law%20put%20the%20%26quot%3Bparty%26quot%3B%20in%20wedding%20party%20of%20which%20they%20all%20were%20members.%20My%20teen%20female