for%20school%20dropouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20in%20Dorset.%20My%20dad%20left%20school%20at%2016%20and%20was%20a%20soldier%20in%20the%20army.%20My%20mum%20worked%20in%20a%20pub%20and%20then%20a%20travel%20agent.%20It%20was%20an%20upbringing%20far%20removed%20from%20London%20and%20the%20world%20of%20finance.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Newton%20had%20been%20the%20first%20in%20his%20family%20to%20be%20offered%20a%20place%20at%20a%20university.%20He%20had%20received%20an%20acceptance%20letter%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Warwick%20to%20study%20maths%2C%20however%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20join%20Brightstart%20so%20that%20he%20could%20get%20an%20early%20start%20and%20earn%20some%20money.%20At%20present%2C%20he%20is%20working%20as%20an%20auditor%20and%20is%20also%20a%20qualified%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fuk%2Fen%2Fpages%2Fcareers%2Farticles%2Ffive-things-that-made-me-ben-newton.html%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Newton%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20place%20at%20Warwick%20University%20to%20study%20maths%2C%20which%20I%20was%20looking%20forward%20to.%20But%20that%20summer%2C%20I%20was%20working%20a%20couple%20of%20jobs%20to%20save%20money%20and%20decided%20to%20research%20grad%20schemes%20to%20work%20out%20what%20I%20might%20want%20to%20do%20after%20uni.%20I%20came%20across%20the%20option%20of%20school-leaver%20schemes%20and%20decided%2C%20for%20good%20practice%2C%20to%20apply%20to%20some%20of%20them%20-%20with%20no%20intention%20of%20deviating%20from%20my%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20landed%20a%20few%20interviews%20and%20one%20of%20them%20was%20from%20Deloitte.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20a%20similar%20role%20after%20university%20and%20I'm%20a%20bit%20impatient%2C%20so%20I%20took%20the%20job.%20I%20love%20learning%20and%20I%20know%20I'd%20have%20loved%20the%20social%20side%20of%20university%2C%20and%