%2F109286198.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussian-supersonic-missile-boat-enters-mediterranean%2Famp_articleshow%2F109286198.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%3A%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Who%20Vowed%20'Revenge'%20On%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20launched%20missiles%20and%20drones%20at%20Israel%20as%20a%20retaliatory%20strike%20for%20a%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20a%20Syrian%20diplomatic%20complex.%20Now%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20of%20Iran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Israeli%20strike%20targeted%20Iran's%20embassy%20in%20Damascus%20on%20April%201%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20had%20warned%20that%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20punished%20and%20will%20be%20punished%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20has%20been%20the%20most%20influential%20leader%20in%20the%20country%20since%201989.%20He%20is%20the%20commander-in-chief%20and%20the%20head%20of%20state%2C%20overseeing%20the%20morality%20police%20and%20the%20national%20police.%20Ali%20Khamenei%20also%20administers%20the%20Islamic%20Revolution%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%2C%20which%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20internal%20security%2C%20and%20its%20volunteer%20branch%2C%20the%20Basij%20Resistance%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20facts%20about%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Ali%20Khamenei%20was%20born%20on%20July%2016%2C%201939%2C%20in%20Mashhad%2C%20a%20Khorasan%20province.%20He%20was%20the%20second%20child%20of%20Islamic%20scholar%20Sayyed%20Javad%20Khamenei%2C%20who%20taught%20his%20family%20members%20to%20lead%20a%20life%20of%20simplicity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Ali%20Khamenei%20Khamenei%20continued%20his%20education%20at%20the%20theological%20seminary%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshrine-of-imam-reza-in-irans-mashhad-once-vi