0rivalry%20that%20emerged%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%201979%20Iranian%20revolution.%20The%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20cities%20last%20year%20and%20Tel%20Aviv's%20brutal%20counterstrike%20triggered%20a%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Iran%20is%20learnt%20to%20be%20backing%20several%20players%20such%20as%20Hezbollah%20in%20their%20offensive%20against%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20attack%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20first%20instance%20in%20which%20Iran%20launched%20a%20strike%20against%20Israel%20from%20its%20own%20soil.%20Tehran%20has%20underlined%20that%20it%20is%20an%20act%20of%20self-defence%20after%20Israel's%20suspected%20attack%20on%20its%20embassy%20in%20Syria's%20Damascus%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Iran%20has%20now%20put%20the%20ball%20in%20Israel's%20court%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20hopes%20there%20would%20be%20no%20further%20escalation%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20matter%20can%20be%20deemed%20concluded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20looking%20at%20factors%20and%20build-up%20leading%20to%20the%20escalation%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Origins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201979%20Iranian%20revolution%2C%20the%20Pahlavi%20dynasty%20that%20had%20aligned%20itself%20with%20the%20US%20was%20overthrown%20and%20a%20theocratic%20dispensation%20led%20by%20Ayatollah%20Ruhollah%20Khomeini%20took%20over.%20Khomeini%20effected%20a%20180-degree%20shift%20in%20Tehran's%20engagement%20with%20the%20US%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20the%20Great%20Satan.%20He%20coined%20the%20epithet%2C%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Satan%26quot%3B%20for%20Israel%20for%20its%20backing%20of%20Mohammad%20Reza%20Pahlavi%2C%20the%20last%20monarch%20of%20Iran%2C%20its%20close%20ties%20with%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20hostilities%20between%20Tehran%20and%20Tel%20Aviv%20increased%2C%20Khomeini%20also%20accused%20Israel%20of%20attempts%20to%20thwart%20Iran's%20nuclear%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20both%20Tehran%20and%20Tel%20Aviv%20have%20attacked%20each%20other%2C%20but%20have%20denied%20their%20hand%20in%20such%20offensives.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20their%20conflict%20has%20been%20termed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshadow%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon%20and%20Syria%20emerged%20as%20two%20battlegrounds%20for%20this%20shadow%20war.%20Iran%20backed%20Hezbollah%2C%20which%20has%20been%20targeting%20Israel%20from%20Lebanese%20soil.%20In%20Syria%2C%20Tehran%20backed%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20as%20Israel%20launched%20airstrikes%20in%20Syrian%20territory.%20Golan%20Heights%2C%20an%20area%20in%20Syria%20occupied%20by%20Israel%20after%20the%201967%20war%2C%20is%20used%20by%20Tel%20Aviv%20for%20its%20attacks%20in%20Syria%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas%20Attacks%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%20Hamas%20operatives%20launched%20a%20shock%20attack%20on%20Israel's%20cities%2C%20killing%20over%201%2C200%20people%20and%20taking%20more%20than%20200%20hostages.%20In%20public%20remarks%2C%20Iran%20denied%20any%20role%20in%20the%20Hamas%20offensive%2C%20but%20welcomed%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel%20cities.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20posters%20with%20messages%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20great%20liberation%20has%20begun%26quot%3B%20came%20up%20in%20prominent%20street%20squares%20in%20Tehran.%20Mutliple%20media%20reports%20said%20Iran%20had%20actively%20backed%20Hamas%20operatives%20in%20planning%20and%20executing%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel's%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%207%20attacks%20triggered%20a%20brutal%20counterstrike%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20which%20launched%20an%20all-out%20offensive%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20According%20to%20UN%20estimates%2C%20more%20than%2033%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20Israeli%20retaliation%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20opened%20another%20front%20by%20launching%20a%20volley%20of%20rockets%20at%20Israel%20from%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Trigger%3A%20Damascus%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%201%2C%20suspected%20Israeli%20warplanes%20bombed%20Iran's%20embassy%20in%20Syria.%20Tehran%20said%20seven%20military%20advisors%2C%20including%20senior%20commanders%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20condemn%20this%20atrocious%20terrorist%20attack%20that%20targeted%20the%20Iranian%20consulate%20building%20in%20Damascus%20and%20killed%20a%20number%20of%20innocents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Syrian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Faisal%20Mekdad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20strike%2C%20an%20Israeli%20military%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20comment%20on%20reports%20in%20the%20foreign%20media.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20UN%20mission%20described%20the%20strike%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bflagrant%20violation%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Charter%2C%20international%20law%2C%20and%20the%20foundational%20principle%20of%20the%20inviolability%20of%20diplomatic%20and%20consular%20premises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20urged%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20condemn%20the%20attack%20and%20said%20Tehran%20reserved%20the%20right%20%26quot%3Bto%20take%20a%20decisive%20response%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20too%2C%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthis%20crime%20will%20not%20pass%20without%20the%20enemy%20receiving%20punishment%20and%20revenge%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Drone%20Offensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20night%2C%20Iran%20launched%20a%20barrage%20of%20drones%20and%20missiles%20targeted%20at%20Israel.%20The%20Iranian%20army%20said%20its%20drone%20and%20missile%20attack%20has%20%26quot%3Bachieved%20all%20its%20objectives%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Honest%20Promise...%20was%20completed%20successfully%20from%20last%20night%20to%20this%20morning%20and%20achieved%20all%20its%20objectives%26quot%3B%2C%20Mohammad%20Bagheri%2C%20Iranian%20armed%20forces'%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20told%20state%20TV%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20defence%20forces%20said%20most%20drones%20and%20missiles%20were%20successfully%20intercepted%20by%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20and%20the%20Arrow%20Aerial%20Defense%20System.%20%26quot%3BWe%20intercepted%2099%25%20of%20the%20threats%20launched%20to%20the%20territory%20of%20Israel.%20It's%20a%20very%20significant%20strategic%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20military%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20ally%20Syria%20said%20it%20was%20putting%20its%20ground-to-air%20defence%20systems%20and%20major%20bases%20on%20high%20alert%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20vowed%20a%20decisive%20response%20and%20said%20Tel%20Aviv%20has%20been%20preparing%20for%20a%20direct%20attack%20by%20Tehran%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20warned%20that%20its%20response%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20much%20larger%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20drone%20strikes%20if%20Israel%20retaliates.%20Iran's%20armed%20forces%20chief%20General%20Mohammad%20Bagheri%20has%20told%20state%20media%20that%20it%20would%20target%20US%20bases%20too%20if%20Washington%20backs%20Israel's%20counterstrike.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713082140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F96ulm3v8_iran-attack-on-israel_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-45-year-old-enmity-then-a-syria-spark-build-up-to-iran-attack-on-israel-5438960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran's%20massive%20drone%20offensive%20against%20Israel%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20nearly%2050-year-old%20rivalry%20that%20emerged%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%201979%20Iranian%20revolution%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%