l%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20Principal%20Brian%20Smith%20and%20Superintendent%20Scott%20Rocco%20of%20Hamilton%20Township%20School%20District%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20teacher's%20profile%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20school%20website%20teacher's%20directory%20following%20her%20arrest.%20Earlier%2C%20it%20mentioned%20that%20she%20had%20been%20working%20at%20the%20school%20for%20seven%20years.%20%E2%80%9CI%20truly%20enjoy%20getting%20to%20know%20the%20students%20here%20and%20helping%20them%20become%20the%20best%20versions%20of%20themselves%20while%20they%20strive%20for%20their%20futures%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20now-deleted%20profile%20page%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713077700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F0780p57_jessica-sawicki-_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarried-us-teacher-caught-having-sex-with-student-in-car-arrested-5438645%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20statement%20on%20the%20school%20district's%20website%20stated%20that%20Ms%20Sawicki%20had%20been%20placed%20on%20administrative%20leave%20from%20her%20%2441%2C000-per-year%20employment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarried-us-teacher-caught-having-sex-with-student-in-car-arrested-5438645%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarried-us-teacher-caught-having-sex-with-student-in-car-arrested-5438645%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarried-us-teacher-caught-having-sex-with-student-in-car-arrested-5438645%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G7%20leaders%20to%20discuss%20Iranian%20attack%20in%20Sunday%20video%20call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713077168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109284391%2Cimgsize-770757.cms