0Ki%20Guarantee'%20Manifesto%2C%20Congress%20Calls%20It%20Apology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20released%20its%20much-awaited%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20this%20morning%2C%20underlining%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20focus%20on%20'GYAN'%20-%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20youth%2C%20farmers%20and%20the%20women.%20With%20a%20bust%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20Constitution%20on%20stage%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20released%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20manifesto%20focus%20on%20four%20pillars%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20--%20women%20power%2C%20youth%20power%2C%20farmers%20and%20the%20poor.%20He%20said%20it%20focuses%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bdignity%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bquality%20of%20life%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20quantity%20of%20opportunity%20as%20well%20as%20the%20quality%20of%20opportunity.%20The%20government%20will%20focus%20on%20taking%20piped%20gas%20to%20all%20homes%20and%20providing%20free%20electricity%20through%20solar%20power%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manifesto%20said%20the%20Centre's%20free%20ration%20scheme%20will%20be%20extended%20by%205%20years.%20The%20government%2C%20it%20said%2C%20will%20focus%20on%20self-reliance%20in%20production%20of%20pulses%2C%20edible%20oils%20and%20vegetables%20to%20stabilise%20price%20and%20protect%20the%20poor's%20plates.%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20and%20the%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%20will%20be%20expanded%20and%20drinking%20water%20supply%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20every%20home%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20the%20annual%20assistance%20of%20Rs%206%2C000%20and%20will%20strengthen%20the%20crop%20insurance%20scheme%20through%20use%20of%20technology.%20The%20document%20said%20the%20government%20will%20continue%20periodic%20hikes%20in%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20for%20crops%2C%20set%20up%20new%20clusters%20for%20production%20of%20essentials%20and%20build%20more%20storage%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Nadda%20gave%20a%20rundown%20of%20the%20BJP%20government's%20achievements%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20in%20power.%20He%20reiterated%20that%20'Modi%20ki%20guarantee'%20--%20the%20BJP's%20key%20poll%20slogan%20--%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20guarantee%20that%20all%20guarantees%20will%20be%20fulfilled%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20the%20BJP%20chief%20said%20that%20while%20developed%20countries%20oscillated%20between%20prioritising%20economy%20and%20the%20health%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20decisive%20steps%20helped%20India%20recover%20from%20the%20impact%20of%20Covid.%20He%20also%20said%20India%20came%20up%20with%20two%20vaccines%20and%20220%20crore%20doses%20within%20nine%20months%20and%20also%20helped%20reach%20the%20shots%20to%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20to%20speak%20was%20Defence%20Minister%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%2027-member%20committee%20that%20had%20prepared%20the%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20the%20BJP's%20pledges%20made%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20had%20been%20fulfilled.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20say%2C%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20listing%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20women%20reservation%20Bill%20and%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple's%20construction%20as%20its%20key%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%20has%20been%20prepared%20on%20the%20basis%20of%2015%20lakh%20suggestions%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20presents%20a%20roadmap%20for%20Viksit%20Bharat%20while%20focusing%20on%20social%20justice.%C2%A0%26quot%3BModi's%20guarantee%20is%20considered%2024%20karat%20gold%2C%20so%20our%20manifesto%20is%20the%20gold%20standard%20of%20manifesto%20for%20parties%20across%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20also%20invited%20several%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Centre's%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20felicitated%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20it%20should%20be%20called%20a%20'Sankalp%20Patra'%20but%20a%20maafinama%20--%20an%20apology.%20%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20they%20said%20they%20will%20constitute%20a%20taskforce%20to%20bring%20black%20money%20back%2C%20but%20what%20they%20brought%20is%20electoral%20bond.%20Instead%20of%20the%20government%20making%20Smart%20Cities%2C%20China%20is%20making%20smart%20cities%20inside%20our%20boundaries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20said%20the%20BJP's%20policy%20is%20to%20lie%20so%20loudly%20that%20people%20believe%20it%20to%20be%20the%20truth.%20She%20said%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%20does%20not%20even%20mention%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20protests%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713075960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fo9ouinqg_bjp-manifesto_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-2024-election-manifesto-focuses-on-uplifting-women-poor-and-youth-5437817%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP's%202024%20Election%20Manifesto%20Focuses%20On%20Uplifting%20Women%2C%20Poor%20And%20Youth%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-2024-election-manifesto-focuses-on-uplifting-women-poor-and-youth-5437817%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2