20any%20threat%20and%20will%20do%20so%20level-headedly%20and%20with%20determination%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Netanyahu's%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas%20Rejected%20Peace%20Deal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20spy%20agency%20Mosaid%20today%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20had%20rejected%20the%20latest%20proposal%20by%20international%20mediators%20for%20a%20truce%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEgypt%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20the%20US%20have%20previously%20acted%20as%20intermediaries%20in%20negotiations%2C%20yet%20a%20viable%20agreement%20has%20proven%20elusive.%20The%20mediators%20aimed%20to%20secure%20a%20ceasefire%20prior%20to%20the%20commencement%20of%20Ramadan%2C%20but%20progress%20halted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Netanyahu%20sanctioned%20a%20fresh%20cycle%20of%20ceasefire%20discussions%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Doha%20and%20Cairo.%20His%20office%20announced%20that%20the%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20conversed%20with%20Mossad%20chief%20David%20Barnea%20regarding%20the%20talks%2C%20though%20it%20did%20not%20specify%20whether%20Mr%20Barnea%20would%20be%20journeying%20to%20either%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%20250%20hostages%20were%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20the%20October%207%20assaults%20on%20Israel%20that%20instigated%20the%20conflict.%20Israel%20estimates%20that%20130%20individuals%2C%20including%2033%20presumed%20dead%2C%20are%20still%20in%20captivity%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20over%20a%20week%20since%20the%20Cairo%20meeting%20-%20Hamas%20has%20rejected%20the%20outline%20that%20was%20tabled%20by%20the%20mediators%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Israeli%20Pm's%20office%20and%20Mossad%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Erime%20Minister's%20Office%20%E2%80%93%20Mossad%20Stateme