r%20since%20Pandya%20was%20announced%20as%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20new%20captain%20in%20place%20of%20India's%20all-format%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024%2C%20the%20controversial%20decision%20has%20received%20widespread%20disappointment%20from%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI's%20newly-appointed%20captain%20has%20been%20booed%20heavily%20at%20various%20stadiums%2C%20including%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20International%20Stadium%20in%20Hyderabad%20as%20well%20at%20Mumbai's%20home%20ground%20-%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20MI%20started%20their%20IPL%202024%20campaign%20with%20three%20consecutive%20losses%20under%20Hardik's%20leadership%20although%20the%20five-time%20IPL%20winners%20have%20bounced%20back%20with%20back-to-back%20wins%20in%20their%20next%20two%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFitness%20and%20finishing%20ability%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Hardik's%20captaincy%2C%20his%20all-round%20form%20and%20finishing%20ability%20have%20been%20under%20scanner%20in%20the%20ongoing%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team's%20limited-overs%20vice-captain%2C%20Hardik%20has%20scored%20129%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20for%20MI%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hard-hitting%20batter%20showed%20glimpses%20of%20regaining%20form%20after%20he%20slammed%20an%20unbeaten%2021%20runs%20off%20just%20six%20balls%20against%20Royals%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20to%20help%20MI%20chase%20down%20197%20in%20just%2015.3%20overs%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20have%20been%20questions%20about%20Hardik's%20fitness%20for%20ICC's%20marquee%20T20%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20all-rounder%20has%20endured%20his%20fair%20share%20of%20fitness%20concerns%20over%20the%20years%20and%20has%20cut%20down%20on%20his%20workload%20with%20the%20ball%20to%20get%20the%20best%20out%20of%20him%20from%20an%20all-round%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat-born%20cricketer%20has%20bowled%20just%20eight%20overs%20in%20five%20matches%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20picking%20just%20a%20solitary%20wicket%20at%20an%20economy%20of%2011.13.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20recently%20made%20a%20comeback%20in%20IPL%202024%20after%20he%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20having%20sustained%20an%20ankle%20injury%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20India%2C%20of%20course%2C%20will%20need%20a%20fully-fit%20Hardik%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn-form%20Shivam%20Dube%20could%20pip%20Hardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hardik's%20all-round%20capabilities%20provide%20Team%20India%20great%20balance%20in%20the%20T20%20format%2C%20if%20he's%20not%20fully%20fit%20then%20the%20likes%20of%20Shivam%20Dube%20and%20Rinku%20Singh%20could%20be%20better%20picks%20as%20finishers%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20fast%20bowler%20Venkatesh%20Prasad%20has%20voiced%20support%20for%20Shivam%20Dube's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShivam%20Dube%20for%20his%20striking%20ability%20against%20spinners%2C%20Surya%20for%20being%20the%20best%20T20%20international%20batter%20and%20Rinku%20Singh%20for%20his%20exceptional%20finishing%20ability.%20It%20will%20be%20great%20if%20India%20finds%20a%20way%20to%20have%20these%203%20in%20the%2011%20in%20the%20T20%20WC.%20With%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%2C%20this%20will%20leave%20a%20spot%20for%20just%20a%20keeper%20batsman.%20Interesting%20to%20see%20how%20it%20pans%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Prasad%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings'%20Shivam%20Dube%20has%20been%20in%20impre