aned.%20The%20polling%20station%20was%20not%20accessible%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperson%20with%20a%20disability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20stairs%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20EVMs%2C%20she%20wondered%20how%20she%20would%20cast%20her%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20officials%20on%20duty%20finally%20guided%20her%20to%20the%20back%20entrance%20which%20he%20claimed%20had%20a%20ramp%20attached.%20She%20rolled%20down%20the%20way%20only%20to%20find%20two%20flimsy%20wooden%20planks%20bridging%20an%20almost%20foot-long%20difference.%20With%20four%20people%20supporting%20her%20wheelchair%2C%20and%20a%20heavy%20feeling%20of%20being%20let%20down%2C%20Kavya%20cast%20her%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201795px)%20100vw%2C%201795px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221795%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20disabled%20man%20being%20helped%20by%20a%20police%20officer%20into%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20March%202022.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437.jpg%201795w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437-500x334.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437-768x513.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437-1536x1025.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347159%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20disabled%20man%20being%20helped%20by%20a%20police%20officer%20into%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBut%20did%20she%20feel%20like%20an%20equal%20citizen%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20home%20to%20the%20largest%20population%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325545%2Fmust-watch-films-and-shows-on-disability-pride-and-representation-in-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Almost%202.21%20percent%20of%20its%20population%20has%20some%20kind%20of%20disability.%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%20which%20was%20implemented%20in%202016%2C%20mandates%20accessibility%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20under%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fceojk.nic.in%2Fpdf%2FLatest_Notifications%2FVoter_Guide_for_PwDs_and_Sr.Citizens.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESection%2011%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20bestows%20the%20responsibility%20on%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20polling%20stations%20are%20accessible%2C%20with%20all%20necessary%20material%20related%20to%20the%20process%20available.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%2C%20as%20many%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1580572%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E6.2%20million%20voters%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20disabilities%20out%20of%20the%20910%20million%20people%20eligible%20to%20cast%20their%20vote.%20The%20same%20report%20states%20that%20the%20motto%20of%20the%20General%20Elections%20of%202019%20was%20%E2%80%98Accessible%20Elections%E2%80%99%20and%20several%20measures%20ranging%20from%20mapping%20electors%20with%20disabilities%20to%20their%20nearest%20polling%20stations%2C%20installing%20ramps%2C%20having%20Braille-embossed%20Electoral%20Photo%20Identity%20Cards%20and%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%2C%20transportation%20facilities%20and%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20to%20make%20the%20process%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-how-general-elections-2019-were-disabled-friendly%2Fstory-sTF7DaxfgJmHapHotY1rOL.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2019%20op-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20The%20Hindustan%20Times%2C%20George%20Abraham%2C%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%2C%20inspirational%20speaker%20and%20disability%20activist%2C%20shared%20his%20experience%20of%20casting%20his%20vote%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20escorted%20him.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20fill%20up%20form%2049A%20since%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20Braille%20and%20relied%20on%20the%20support%20of%20his%20spouse%20to%20assist%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20following%20weeks%2C%20my%20colleagues%20and%20I%20spoke%20to%20several%20blind%20and%20visually%20impaired%20people%20from%20across%20the%20country%20regarding%20their%20voting%20experience.%20Many%20were%20appreciative%20of%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20in%20making%20these%20elections%20accessible%2C%20while%20some%20cribbed%20of%20insensitive%20officials.%20There%20were%20a%20few%20booths%20where%20the%20Braille%20list%20of%20candidates%20was%20missing.%20But%20overall%2C%20these%20elections%20have%20been%20a%20tremendous%20improvement%20as%20far%20as%20inclusion%20of%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20was%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes%20in%20the%20article.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20call%20for%20accessible%20elections%20by%20civil%20society%20organisations%20as%20well%20as%20from%20within%20the%20ECI%20has%20become%20stronger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20momentum%20of%20accessible%20elections%20got%20high%20within%20ECI%20as%20well%20as%20across%20the%20country%20when%20National%20Voters%20Day%20in%202018%20embraced%20its%20theme%20as%20Accessible%20Elections.%20At%20ECI%2C%20we%20had%20continuous%20discussions%20and%20worked%20on%20all%20possible%20facilitations%20at%20the%20polling%20stations%20to%20ensure%20hassle-free%20voting%20by%20our%20citizens%20with%20disabilities%2C%20thereby%20ECI%20issued%20a%20set%20of%20notifications%2F%20circulars%20on%20the%20same%20to%20all%20Chief%20Election%20Officers.%20I%20also%20facilitated%20the%20inclusion%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20persons%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20the%20system%20to%20the%20ground%20level%20through%20their%20inclusion%20in%20Committees%20for%20accessible%20elections%20from%20national%20to%20state%2C%20district%2C%20and%20AC%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smitha%20Sadasivan%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20Accessibility%20Consultant%20in%20the%20Disability%20Legislation%20Unit%20of%20Vidya%20Sagar%20in%20Chennai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20by%20the%20Government%20to%20leave%20no%20one%20behind%2C%20gaps%20still%20exist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20the%20gaps%20are%20in%20the%20right%20understanding%20of%20accessibility%20itself%2C%20its%20standards%20and%20facilitations%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20for%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20capacity%20building%20is%20needed%20within%20the%20election%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smitha%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPoling-booth-Infographic-1712912046.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPoling-booth-Infographic-1712912046.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPoling-booth-Infographic-1712912046-300x153.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPoling-booth-Infographic-1712912046-500x255.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPoling-booth-Infographic-1712912046-768x392.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPoling-booth-Infographic-1712912046-150x77.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%202019%20was%20termed%20as%20the%20Year%20of%20Accessible%20Elections%2C%20this%20year%20is%20one%20step%20ahead%20with%20the%20government%20now%20offering%20the%20facility%20to%20%E2%80%98Vote%20from%20Home%E2%80%99%20or%20VfH%20to%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20over%2040%25%2C%20and%20those%20aged%2080%20and%20above.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%2C%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20as%20well%20as%20senior%20citizens%20over%2085%20can%20register%20to%20vote%20from%20their%20homes%20using%20a%20postal%20ballot.%20This%20accommodation%20is%20only%20extended%20to%20people%20who%20register%20to%20do%20so%20in%20advance.%20The%20voters%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312600%2Fhow-can-india-be-more-disabled-friendly-inclusive-planning-in-public-events%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20use%20of%20this%20amenity%3C%2Fa%3E%20need%20to%20have%20appropriate%20paperwork%20proving%20their%20disability%2Fage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20process%20to%20register%20is%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1.%20Make%20sure%20that%20you%20have%20the%20necessary%20paperwork.%20For%20persons%20with%20disability%2C%20this%20would%20be%20a%20Unique%20Disability%20Identification%20Card%20(UDID)%20and%20a%20valid%20proof%20of%20age%20matching%20the%20voter%20list%20with%20their%20Polling%20Booth%20for%20Senior%20Citizens.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2.%20Fill%20a%20Form%2012D%20%E2%80%93%20Letter%20of%20intimation%20to%20Assistant%20Returning%20Officer%20(for%20absentee%20voters)%20and%20submit%20it%20to%20your%20respective%20Booth%20Level%20Officers.%20You%20can%20download%20the%20form%20using%20this%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fold.eci.gov.in%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2F12269-form-12d-letter-of-intimation-to-assistant-returning-officer-for-absentee-voters%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20link%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E3.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20Booth%20Level%20Officers%20from%20your%20polling%20booth%20will%20visit%20your%20home%20once%20after%20the%20last%20date%20for%20withdrawal%20of%20nominations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E4.%20In%20the%20event%20that%20the%20voter%20is%20not%20available%20at%20home%2C%20they%20will%20return%20once%20more%20before%2026%20April%20(the%20last%20day%20of%20polling%20for%20this%20cycle%20of%20elections).%20If%20the%20voter%20is%20not%20available%20for%20the%20second%20time%20as%20well%2C%20they%20will%20lose%20their%20opportunity%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E5.%20Please%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20once%20a%20voter%20has%20applied%20for%20a%20postal%20ballot%2C%20they%20no%20longer%20have%20the%20option%20to%20vote%20in%20person%20at%20the%20polling%20booth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20postal%20ballots%20will%20be%20counted%20separately%20from%20the%20votes%20cast%20at%20polling%20booths%20and%20will%20be%20carried%20by%20the%20Booth%20Level%20Officers%20in%20a%20sealed%20envelope%20to%20ensure%20secrecy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20case%20you%20need%20any%20more%20details%20about%20facilities%20for%20PwD%20voters%2C%20you%20can%20get%20them%20on%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20official%20page%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fold.eci.gov.in%2Fpersons-with-disabilities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20speak%20to%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20you%20can%20call%20at%201950%20between%209%20am%20and%209%20pm.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Contributed%20by%20V-shesh%3B%20Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712929599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fshutterstock_2136243787_11zon-1712911437.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%202016%20mandates%20accessibility%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20for%20every%20Indian%20with%20a%20disability.%20Here's%20a%20step-by-step%20guide%20on%20how%20you%2C%20or%20someone%20you%20know%2C%20can%20exercise%20their%20voting%20right.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347158%2Fgeneral-elections-2024-voting-rights-for-persons-with-disabilities-in-india-theme-accessible-elections%2F%22%2C