in%20my%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20spare%20books%20that%20you%20want%20to%20donate%20to%20the%20eatery%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Pravin%20at%209922946622%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Pravin)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712827324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-1-1710406948.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nashik's%20Bhimabai%20Jondhale%20always%20loved%20reading%20but%20never%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20tend%20to%20her%20passion.%20Today%2C%20she%20runs%20'Ajjichya%20Pustakancha%20Hotel'%2C%20a%20unique%20book%20hotel%20which%20serves%20delicious%20meals%20along%20with%20free%20books%20to%20read!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344848%2Fnashik-bhimabai-jondhale-ajjichya-pustakancha-hotel-book-hotel-by-grandmother%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20One%20Woman%20Created%20an%20Army%20of%2075000%20Others%20to%20Fight%20Trafficking%20of%20Girls%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Pallabi%20Ghosh%20was%2012%20years%20old%2C%20she%20encountered%20her%20first%20case%20of%20a%20child%20from%20a%20nearby%20village%20being%20trafficked.%20This%20shaped%20her%20decision%20to%20dedicate%20her%20life%20to%20rescuing%20children%20who%20were%20victims%20of%20this%20horrific%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%2C%20Pallabi%20founded%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313315%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-rescue-children-from-trafficking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImpact%20and