20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247633%2Fla-kheer-deli-shivang-sood-pune-startup-kheer-indian-traditional-dessert-homemade-recipes-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreamy%20concoctions%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20fit%20for%20kings.%20Once%20prepared%20for%20royalty%2C%20the%20dish%20reflects%20regional%20sensibilities%2C%20with%20each%20diaspora%20adding%20to%20it%20what%20they%20deem%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20origins%20of%20the%20vermicelli%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20ingredients%20in%20%3Cem%3Eseviyan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20are%20hidden%20by%20the%20passage%20of%20time.%20Translating%20to%20%E2%80%98little%20worms%E2%80%99%2C%20these%20thin%20rice%20noodles%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20diets%20as%20far%20back%20as%20the%201660s.%20And%2C%20each%20cuisine%20has%20embraced%20a%20different%20form%20of%20it%20in%20its%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20706px)%20100vw%2C%20706px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-08-190421-1712583287.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Seviyan%20is%20a%20milk-based%20delicacy%20that%20is%20often%20prepared%20around%20Eid%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-08-190421-1712583287.jpg%20706w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-08-190421-1712583287-298x300.jpg%20298w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-08-190421-1712583287-500x504.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-08-190421-1712583287-150x151.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-08-190421-1712583287-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3